{
  "texts": [
    "IntroductionIn an era of globalization, English language education is essential for personal growth, professional development, and international communication.",
    "As a globally used language, English allows learners with another native language to communicate with people from other countries with fewer barriers, enabling them to participate effectively and benefit from international activities or projects.",
    "Due to the value attached to language education, researchers are discovering methods of adopting technology into language education and using them to stimulate learner's studying interests [1].In recent years, Large Language Models (LLM) and their fast development have drawn attention from educators.",
    "As a branch of Artificial Intelligence (AI), LLMs aim to train models that can understand and generate human-like language.",
    "These models are featured by their massive numbers of parameters and diverse training datasets, and they demonstrate good performance on human-level text generations and relative tasks [2].Due to LLMs' strong functions, they are already used in education and have a profound impact."
  ]
}